{"tid":308070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巫山夢醒拒玩一夜情　猴急男打差人發洩被捕","createTime":"2017-07-04T00:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T02:35:58.000Z","uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0c4906c846c201842bf024b208f84c839d9719","tid":308070,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:24:07.000Z","msg":"7月 4日(二) 04:43<br />\n<strong>巫山夢醒拒玩一夜情　猴急男打差人發洩被捕</strong><br />\n<br />\n年約20餘歲身穿黑T恤男子，今晨3時許在尖沙咀金巴利道一酒吧，結識一名黑衣女郎，相邀共享一夜情，隨即飛的返沙田男子家中，不料疑有人在坐車途中摸手摸腳，女子既驚且怒出言拒絕赴約，並向的哥表示要折返荃灣住所；男子聞言亦甚為不悅，雙方頓起爭執。的士司機見狀，將車駛至九龍塘窩打老道近添福道巴士站報案求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場調查，男子採取不合作態度，推撞警員，糾纏間一名警員手腳扭傷，數名同袍隨即將男子制服，他涉嫌襲警被捕帶署扣查，黑衣女則獲邀返署助查，受傷警員則送院治理。"},{"pid":"0619a1d70bb370e7063ca8cc968bb88a5c6b5175","tid":308070,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"黑警R工傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f5e4c676d46a51c51f0b90cbc0704aef77b46e","tid":308070,"uid":64636,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:30:33.000Z","msg":"正評比條題<br />\n好中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae401ea8e0a0dccf845d01ccb9302a676fe29e5b","tid":308070,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:49:56.000Z","msg":"條女做乜鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0cdf1db31d8b2e9a19c351611599d977d44eb4","tid":308070,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:53:29.000Z","msg":"係咪想慳的士錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔明點解玩玩下又要唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e1be317ecb217d0172b149c335caee442f7b3b","tid":308070,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:57:47.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"9c79c684112c4df156d3d411a0e72fabfabe404f","tid":308070,"uid":4972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco